  <h2 style="text-align:left"><strong>Program Guidelines</strong></p>

 <p class="italics" style="text-align:left"><i> Program Guidelines
After completion of training, the participant employee must attain one of the program outcomes:</i></p>
  
   <ul style="text-align:left">
        <li><p style="text-align:left">Shift to new job duties utilizing their new skill set,</p></li>
       <li><p style="text-align:left">Gain a new job title,</p></li>
         <li><p style="text-align:left">Receive an increase in compensation, OR</p></li>
